Package com.archibus.datasource.data

This package contains the DataSource data classes.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
DataRecord Encapsulates a single database record.
DataRecordField Data Transfer object for record values, used by web services.
DataSet Base class for data sets that can be serialized to the client.
DataSet1D Data set containing a list of records grouped by one dimension.
DataSet2D Data set containing a list of records grouped by one dimension.
DataSetGrid Specialized data set for report grid/mini-console controls.
DataSetList Data set containing a list of records.
DataValue Encapsulates database field value as a Java object.
 

Package com.archibus.datasource.data Description

This package contains the DataSource data classes.
